        "content": "<h3>We are living in an API-centric world. APIs are everywhere, and you might not even realize it. Gartner considers API-based digital management tools as a critical architectural approach to integrate and connect with anything that has a digital pulse. Forrester also estimates that almost 40% of US-based companies will implement solutions meant at handling the increasing demand for APIs in their organizations, making API-based digital commerce essential to your digital commerce strategy.</h3>\n",
